{"name": "agi-med-protos", "metadata": {"name": "agi-med-protos", "version": "1.1.0", "classifiers": [], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["grpcio", "grpcio-tools"], "summary": "GRPC utils for agi-med team", "upload_time": 1733480654}, "documentation": ["# agi-med-utils\n\n\u0421\u0442\u0430\u043d\u0434\u0430\u0440\u0442\u0438\u0437\u0438\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0430\u043d\u043d\u044b\u0439 \u043a\u043e\u043c\u043f\u043e\u043d\u0435\u043d\u0442 GRPC \u043a\u043b\u0438\u0435\u043d\u0442\u043e\u0432 \u043e\u0431\u0449\u0435\u0439 \u0431\u0438\u0431\u043b\u0438\u043e\u0442\u0435\u043a\u0438 \u043e\u0442\u0434\u0435\u043b\u0430\n\n## \u041e\u0442\u0432\u0435\u0442\u0441\u0442\u0432\u0435\u043d\u043d\u044b\u0439 \u0440\u0430\u0437\u0440\u0430\u0431\u043e\u0442\u0447\u0438\u043a\n\n@bakulin\n\n## \u041e\u0431\u0449\u0430\u044f \u0438\u043d\u0444\u043e\u0440\u043c\u0430\u0446\u0438\u044f\n\n### \u0424\u0438\u0447\u0438:\n\n- \u0410\u0431\u0441\u0442\u0440\u0430\u043a\u0442\u043d\u044b\u0439 grpc \u043a\u043b\u0438\u0435\u043d\u0442\n\n## \u0422\u0435\u0441\u0442\u044b\n\n- `sudo docker-compose up --build`\n\n### \u041b\u0438\u043d\u0442\u0435\u0440\u044b\n\n```shell\npip install black flake8-pyproject mypy\nblack .\nflake8\nmypy .\n```\n\n\u0438\u043b\u0438 \u0447\u0435\u0440\u0435\u0437 pre-commit\n\n```shell\npip install pre-commit\npre-commit install\npre-commit run --all-files # \u043f\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0435\u0440\u043a\u0430 \u0432\u0440\u0443\u0447\u043d\u0443\u044e\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "agi_med_protos.header_client", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "agi_med_protos.header_client.R", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "agi_med_protos.header_client.H", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "agi_med_protos.header_client.HeaderClient", "bases": ["BasicClient"], "methods": [{"name": "agi_med_protos.header_client.HeaderClient.__call__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "request", "type": {"name": "R", "xref": {"fqname": "R", "project": null}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "agi_med_protos.header_client.HeaderClient._generate_metadata", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "headers", "type": {"name": "H", "xref": {"fqname": "H", "project": null}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "**_", "type": {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "list", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.list", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "tuple", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.tuple", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, {"name": "DictValue", "xref": {"fqname": "DictValue", "project": null}, "params": null}]}]}, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["\u0411\u0430\u0437\u043e\u0432\u044b\u0439 \u043a\u043b\u0430\u0441\u0441, \u043a\u043e\u0442\u043e\u0440\u044b\u0439 \u043e\u0434\u043d\u0438\u043c \u0438\u0437 \u043f\u0430\u0440\u0430\u043c\u0435\u0442\u0440\u043e\u0432 \u0437\u0430\u043f\u0440\u043e\u0441\u0430 \u043f\u0440\u0438\u043d\u0438\u043c\u0430\u0435\u0442 Headers.\n\u041d\u0438\u0436\u0435 \u043f\u0440\u0435\u0434\u0441\u0442\u0430\u0432\u043b\u0435\u043d \u043f\u0440\u0438\u043c\u0435\u0440 \u043d\u0430\u0441\u043b\u0435\u0434\u043e\u0432\u0430\u043d\u0438\u044f \u043a\u043b\u0430\u0441\u0441\u0430\n\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass\nfrom typing import Any\n\nfrom agi_med_protos.dto import Headers, RequestWithHeaders\nfrom agi_med_protos.header_client import HeaderClient, DictValue\n\n\n\nclass FooHeaders(Headers):\n    some_value: str\n\n\n@dataclass\nclass FooRequest(RequestWithHeaders[FooHeaders]):\n    text: str\n\n\nclass FooClient(HeaderClient[FooRequest, FooHeaders]):\n    def __call__(self, request: FooRequest) -> float:\n        metadata: list[tuple[str, DictValue]] = self._generate_metadata(request.headers, request.text)\n        print(metadata)\n        return 0.91\n\n    def _generate_metadata(\n            self, headers: FooHeaders, text: str | None = None, **_: Any\n    ) -> list[tuple[str, DictValue]]:\n        if text is None:\n            text = \"really_need_information\"\n        headers[\"additional_headers\"] = {\n            \"text\": text\n        }\n        return super()._generate_metadata(headers)"]}], "exports": []}, {"name": "agi_med_protos", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "agi_med_protos.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "agi_med_protos.AbstractClient", "xref": {"fqname": "agi_med_protos.abstract_client.AbstractClient", "project": null}}, {"name": "agi_med_protos.BasicClient", "xref": {"fqname": "agi_med_protos.basic_client.BasicClient", "project": null}}, {"name": "agi_med_protos.HeaderClient", "xref": {"fqname": "agi_med_protos.header_client.HeaderClient", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "agi_med_protos.basic_client", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "agi_med_protos.basic_client.T", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "agi_med_protos.basic_client.BasicClient", "bases": ["AbstractClient"], "methods": [{"name": "agi_med_protos.basic_client.BasicClient.__call__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "request", "type": {"name": "T", "xref": {"fqname": "T", "project": null}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inne